{"tid":1682822,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"示威活動持續，為何香港股市無大變化?","createTime":"2019-10-30T09:45:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T15:03:43.000Z","uid":308595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4842e9fce55dd75d5cba160106c23a87c8ce26ba","tid":1682822,"uid":308595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:45:41.000Z","msg":"示威活動持續4個多月，<br />\n為何香港股市無大變化?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">原因?</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef33f4c92c0fb6153349cfeae86afa9776f5815","tid":1682822,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:46:57.000Z","msg":"中共印銀紙托市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bfb9fda60aecb47a786e4a5720146e02bd1c1e2","tid":1682822,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:47:30.000Z","msg":"更細更分散嘅攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1677737\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1677737</a><br />\n睇落去啲留言有講點做<br />\n旺旺, 青島, 獅球嘜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66a547281ae60b06e5d99654b3572cb2022be4dc","tid":1682822,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:49:17.000Z","msg":"其實要達成目標<br />\n不外乎都係開源節流<br />\n開源，好簡單，姐係要令對方加入己方陣營<br />\n都係教育佢地民主是個好東西<br />\n<br />\n但有d 長者唔會明<br />\n咁呢個時候就要節流<br />\n佢地班口撐支那唔緊要<br />\n肉體懼怕支那先最實際<br />\n正如有d 人口裡反美心，身體卻去食元氣<br />\n呢d 真係唔太實際囉<br />\n<br />\n為左節流<br />\n大家快d share 文宣比長者睇<br />\n支那嘅恐怖真係隨時影響到香港<br />\n到時棺材都無埋就好笑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E3ADQhD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE3ADQhD.jpg&h=fbfa3f8a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7L003CF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7L003CF.jpg&h=0bf8c277&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5fcea3ef051b75189a8c26cfbbe0b07f14297843","tid":1682822,"uid":308595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ef33f4c92c0fb6153349cfeae86afa9776f5815","tid":1682822,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:46:57.000Z","msg":"中共印銀紙托市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:52:06.000Z","msg":"點托，托埋我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07801612a7f5b821798be3ab20da35c547f08017","tid":1682822,"uid":287547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:58:20.000Z","msg":"營業模式:  <br />\n<br />\n<strong>根據手足經濟能力的不同</strong>:   <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">經濟能力充裕</span> ----&gt; 以 <strong>正常價格</strong> 購買貨品 ----&gt; 令店鋪能持續經營 ----&gt; 擴充并聘請義士 + 利潤支持長期抗爭   <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">手足有需要幫手</span> ----&gt; 利用優惠碼以 <strong>成本價</strong> 購買貨品(注1) ----&gt; 手足減輕生活成本 ----&gt; 可支配收入增加 <br />\n<br />\n[榮光歸港人互助計劃] 讓有需要既手足都能以成本價買野 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1681328\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1681328</a> <br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"edacce3652e1d464fb5e9330883d571c4f4cb31d","tid":1682822,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:03:43.000Z","msg":"啲細股跌左幾倍<br />\n托恆指, 國企<br />\n所以睇落冇大變化"}]}